Terms & Conditions | Privacy Policy

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

At Digi Medical Sewa, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our customers and website visitors. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose personal information and data that we receive from users of our website and customers of our products and services. By using our website or purchasing our products or services, you consent to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this policy.

1. What information do we collect?

We may collect personal information and data from you in various ways, including when you visit our website, register for an account, make a purchase, subscribe to our newsletter, or contact us for support. The types of personal information we may collect include:
Name, address, email address, and phone number
Login credentials, such as username and password
Usage data, such as pages visited and time spent on our website
Communication preferences and feedback
Other information you choose to provide to us


2. How do we use your information?

We may use the personal information we collect from you for the following purposes:
To process and fulfill your orders and requests
To communicate with you about your orders, products, and services
To send you marketing communications and promotional offers
To improve our website and products and services
To provide customer support and respond to your inquiries
To protect our website and customers from fraudulent activity
To comply with legal obligations and enforce our policies
How do we protect your information?

We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety and security of your personal information. These measures include using SSL encryption to protect sensitive information, restricting access to personal information to only authorized personnel, and regularly monitoring our systems for vulnerabilities and threats.

3. Do we share your information with third parties?

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties without your consent, except as necessary to provide products or services that you have requested or to comply with legal requirements. We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website and conducting our business, such as payment processors and shipping carriers. These third-party providers have access to your personal information only to perform specific tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use your information for any other purpose.

4. Do we use cookies?

Yes, we use cookies to enhance your browsing experience on our website. Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit our website. They enable us to recognize your browser and remember your preferences, such as language settings and shopping cart items. We also use cookies to collect usage data and analyze website performance. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but this may limit your access to certain features of our website.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. We will post the updated policy on our website and indicate the date of the last revision. Your continued use of our website or products and services after any changes to this policy constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please email us at info@digimedicalsewa,com. We will respond to your inquiry as soon as possible.
